      • setCanceledOnTouchOutside

        public MaterialDialog setCanceledOnTouchOutside(boolean cancel)
        Sets whether this dialog is canceled when touched outside the window's bounds OR pressed the back key. If setting to true, the dialog is set to be cancelable if not already set.
        参数:
        cancel - Whether the dialog should be canceled when touched outside the window OR pressed the back key.
